description: Scattered about the clearing are colorfully painted urns filled with bright blossoms.  Several carved stone benches are nestled into small alcoves created by the thick greenery that encircles the area.  Hanging from one of the tree branches high above are a series of windchimes crafted from lengths of copper.
title: [Valley of Gold, Bazaar]
location: between Wehnimer's Landing and Zul Logoth
